>\n<br />\n業界希望政府舉辦「肉類分割技術員」培訓課程，吸引新血，課程內容包括豬肉部位分類和屠宰知識，及為學員提供就業機會。勞工及福利局長張建宗承諾增撥資源，由僱員再培訓局開辦免費全日制肉類切割技術員課程，學員每日可獲153.8元津貼；又鼓勵業界擴闊聘用領域，吸納60至70歲人士、少數族裔、更生人士及輕度殘障者。<br />\n<br />\n其實，鮮肉處理行業人工日薪計900至1,000港元不等，月入可逾2萬港元，而且處理工序非機器可取代，工作機會穩定，行業環境不如外界所想艱辛，年輕一輩大可考慮投身這個偉大的行業！<br />\n<br />\n*有關課程詳情請向僱員再培訓局查詢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">未讀完個課程啊</span>"},{"pid":"164fce20c52c68e4fe31c4bfbdf037e4d5202c0b","tid":1397793,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"假文宣都話要塞三隧！各位小心！！<br />\n<br />\n義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第11頁有藍絲假文宣合集</strong></span><br />\n補番真文宣source<br />\n5/8 全港大三罷+ 7區開🌼 公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveinghkgrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsaveinghkgrp&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=67ff932c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveinghkgrp</a>"},{"pid":"6bef02bbb505f8a688a46ae8fc3b45f67f63136a","tid":1397793,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea6482f776fb1052a2e6bae18f4d7450fcb7f23e","tid":1397793,"uid":60626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:44:20.000Z","msg":"人地提早郷應罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e6dd44b812f3390aef1e497670c2d799c0bbf6","tid":1397793,"uid":60626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea6482f776fb1052a2e6bae18f4d7450fcb7f23e","tid":1397793,"uid":60626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:44:20.000Z","msg":"人地提早郷應罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB